### CheckPoint — Admin Games endpoints
### Requires an ADMIN account. See admin-users.http for the login request.

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api
@token = PASTE_YOUR_ADMIN_JWT_HERE

### Search external games (IGDB) by title
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/external-games/search?query=zelda&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Import a single external game by its external (IGDB) id
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/games/import/1020
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Bulk import the top-rated games (async job)
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/games/import/top-rated?limit=100&minRatingCount=100
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Bulk import recently released games (async job)
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/games/import/recent?limit=100
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Poll the status of a bulk import job
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/games/import/jobs/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Manually create a game
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/games
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "My Manual Game",
  "description": "A game entered manually by an admin.",
  "coverUrl": "https://example.com/cover.jpg",
  "artworkUrl": "https://example.com/artwork.jpg",
  "trailerYoutubeId": "dQw4w9WgXcQ",
  "timeToBeatNormally": 1200,
  "timeToBeatHastily": 600,
  "timeToBeatCompletely": 3000,
  "releaseDate": "2024-05-01",
  "genreIds": [],
  "platformIds": [],
  "companyIds": []
}

### Update a game
PUT {{baseUrl}}/admin/games/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated Game Title",
  "description": "Updated description.",
  "coverUrl": "https://example.com/cover.jpg",
  "artworkUrl": "https://example.com/artwork.jpg",
  "trailerYoutubeId": "dQw4w9WgXcQ",
  "timeToBeatNormally": 1200,
  "timeToBeatHastily": 600,
  "timeToBeatCompletely": 3000,
  "releaseDate": "2024-05-01",
  "genreIds": [],
  "platformIds": [],
  "companyIds": []
}

### Delete a game
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/admin/games/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
